Andy Murray has been confirmed as the No 8 seed for the US Open, which begins on August 25.

Murray was set to be seeded No 9 until the withdrawal of defending champion Rafael Nadal through injury on Monday moved the Brit up one place.

However, it is still Murray's lowest Grand Slam seeding since he was No 12 at Wimbledon 2008.

