The women's seedings will be announced on Wednesday, with the draw scheduled for Thursday. 

Dan Cox and Naomi Broady both play their first-round qualifying matches in New York on Tuesday.

Fellow Brits James Ward, Dan Evans and Dan Smethurst open their campaigns on Wednesday. 

